<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to SkillBridge</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f5f7ff; color: #1a1a2e; line-height: 1.6; }
        .wrapper { width: 100%; background-color: #f5f7ff; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(99,102,241,0.08); border: 1px solid #e8eaf6; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #4f46e5 100%); padding: 48px 40px 40px; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 14px; }
        .content { padding: 40px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1a1a2e; }
        .message { font-size: 15px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .feature-grid { margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .feature-item { padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f7ff; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #6366f1; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .feature-item h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #4f46e5; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .feature-item p { font-size: 13px; color: #666; }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #4f46e5 100%); color: #ffffff !important; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer { background-color: #f5f7ff; padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e8eaf6; }
        .footer p { font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .header { padding: 32px 24px; }
            .content { padding: 24px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Welcome to<br/>SkillBridge.</h1>
                <p>Learn. Teach. Grow.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="greeting">Hey <%= name %>,</div>
                <p class="message">
                    We're thrilled to have you join the SkillBridge community! Your journey to smarter learning and teaching starts now.
                </p>
                <div class="feature-grid">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>Find Expert Tutors</h3>
                        <p>Browse hundreds of skilled tutors and book 1-on-1 sessions instantly.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>Explore Courses</h3>
                        <p>Discover structured courses created by top institutes and mentors.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>Track Your Progress</h3>
                        <p>Manage your bookings, reviews, and learning history in one place.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta-button">Explore Your Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>© 2026 SkillBridge. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>This email was sent to <%= email %>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
